description: The Microsoft Real-time Media Platform enables bots to interact with Skype and Microsoft Teams calls and Microsoft Teams meetings using real-time voice, video and screen sharing. This is an advanced capability which allows the bot to send and receive voice and video content frame by frame. The bot has "raw" access to the voice, video and screen sharing media streams.
